{"tid":1326087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要！】暫時唔好用彩彈","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T13:58:39.000Z","uid":232766,"like":12,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f802b1e5344d52c6a8cf54b5718326323ddad065","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:48:36.000Z","msg":"（以下純粹係 wargame 討論，一方扮警察，一方扮暴民，有啲扮記者）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>警方依家好想用顏色水嚟射群眾</strong></span><br />\n但個畫面太難睇，又可能整到記者<br />\n如果貿貿然用，到時又俾人屌到反轉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果係示威者<ins><strong>先用</strong></ins>彩彈<br />\n輿論又會好唔同<br />\n警方就大條道理用顏色水</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以就算係用，都等到對方先用第一次<br />\n到下一次出嚟先用</span><br />\n而坦白講，彩彈攻擊／破壞力都唔算大<br />\n用與唔用分別未必好大<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>記住，顏色水好難洗<br />\n除非你住樓上或由頭包到落腳（兼可以換衫）<br />\n否則好難搞</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個對保護前線相當重要，請幫推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa56b44b5beae78b036c8d92e3c1b12d11a83441","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f62e01e31579023a2a11ee232d52a532d290ba73","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af910523057f6edd9261fc6eb4e192e4c684f139","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"974359cd09f63f7767a2ae43a390b2b4a67f9c6f","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a70182a2a3e3f205235158e9f19a54d5e7f85950","tid":1326087,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76a2c31f467d364101401c4a58d211266c74b88f","tid":1326087,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl